data.description: Come take a look at this stunning Lantana model, the proud SILVER Winner of the 2022 Triangle Parade of Homes Gala! Sunlight streams through the open floor concept, creating a perfect space for effortless entertaining in the living and dining areas. Imagine whipping up culinary masterpieces in the chef's dream kitchen, boasting a restaurant-grade gas stove, a walk-in pantry fit for a gourmand, and a sprawling island ideal for casual meals and conversation. Step outside to your nearly half-acre blank canvas, ready to be transformed into your own outdoor oasis. Picture a sparkling pool surrounded by lush landscaping, a cozy fire pit for starlit evenings, or a flourishing vegetable garden nurtured by your green thumb. The possibilities are endless! This award-winning home is truly something special, and it won't be on the market for long. Schedule your showing today and experience the magic for yourself!
